<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，毛克利回到了山洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈觉得有什么不对劲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了，儿子？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利不想跟狼妈妈谈别的狼们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，有只蝙蝠在聊谢尔坎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在附近打猎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，我打算今晚在人类的田地附近打猎。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，毛克利就匆匆离开，穿过灌木丛向下跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在山谷底的小溪附近，他听见了喊声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是狼们在打猎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跳上去！阿克拉！” 一只年轻的狼喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我们看看你的力量！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利听见牙齿折断的声音，然后是一声尖叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉跑向了什么，却错过了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利朝村庄跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利从来没有离村庄这么近过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄地走进一个村舍，仔细地朝里面看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红花在一面墙上闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利看见一个女人起身吹了一下红花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，女人往红花里放了些树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红花很危险。他该怎么办呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他等了一个晚上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，他看见一个小孩儿拿起了一个火盆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男孩儿在里面放满了一块块火红的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个小男孩儿能碰那红花。”他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我也能！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利冲向男孩儿，抢走了那个火盆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他朝森林深处跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，毛克利停下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像那个女人那样朝红色东西吹气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，该给它吃东西了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利往红花上放了树枝和树皮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，红花就又燃烧起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利笑了。“我成功了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走到半山坡的时候，他见到了巴希拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑豹看起来很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿克拉昨晚打猎失败了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼们想杀了他，但他们在找你呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在山谷里来着。我准备好战斗了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利举起了装着火的火盆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉点了点头。“很好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他更仔细地看了看那红花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怕这个东西吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它开花的时候，很危险。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不害怕，实际上，我很久以前就记得它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在我成为狼之前，我在离红花很近的地方休息，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又暖和，又幸福。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，毛克利朝狼群会议走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站在后面，狼群看不见火盆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利看见空荡荡的岩石，咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在打猎中受伤的阿克拉躺在岩石旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从头狼的位子上被赶下来了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎从岩石后面走了出来，年轻的狼们跟着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当全体都到时，谢尔坎开始讲话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他没有权利在这里讲话！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉生气地对毛克利低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利一下子站起来。“为什么他......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“安静，人类孩子！”一些狼喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉慢慢地抬起了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我又弱又老。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一只狼要和我战斗，成为狼群的新头狼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼们沉默了很久，谁也不想和阿克拉战斗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只想要那个人类孩子。”谢尔坎咆哮道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把那个人类孩子给我，我就不干涉你的狼群了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把毛克利交给老虎吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只狼喊道，“毛克利不是狼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉又抬起头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利吃我们的食物，跟我们睡在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他没有违反森林法则。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是我们的兄弟。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，他是个人类！”狼群咆哮着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎甩了一下尾巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉看了一眼毛克利。“现在！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利站直了，把火盆拿给狼群看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>339955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们经常告诉我，我不是狼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，我不会再把你们当做我的兄弟姐妹了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把火盆扔在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>351705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红花很快就燃烧了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>